                        <condition key="deficient">The Ms. consists of ate least several Mss.
                           fragments put together. The front and back boards are broken; it is
                           difficult to understand to which of the Mss. the boards originally
                           belonged.&#xD; The sewing is destroyed and has been repaired with several
                           threads.&#xD; The Ms. is damaged by rodents with loss of text, e.g., on
                              <locus target="#64">64</locus>, 77, 101, 113, &#xD; The Ms. is
                           severely affected by humidity. Many leaves are discoloured; many are
                           stained with water (e.g., <locus target="#30v">30v</locus>, 35r, 49v,
                           85v), text on many leaves (e.g., <locus target="#31rb">31rb</locus>,
                           41va, 57va, 66va, 85ra) is barely legible or illegible.&#xD; Many leaves
                           are misplaced, some are missing, some texts are incomplete.&#xD; Many
                           leaves are held together by parchment strips sewn in the margin: e.g.,
                              <locus from="64" to="71">64-71</locus>, 72-78.&#xD; Tears amended on
                              <locus target="#32">32</locus>, 99, 106.</condition>
